    "In the fourth stage, the data analyzed in the previous stage is used to determine whether the change can be adopted and to plan the next PDSA cycle.",
    "In a broader sense, the PDSA model provides an analogy to describe the process involved in an intervention to limit inappropriate use of laboratory resources, and can be used to develop effective and sustainable interventions (Fig. 2).",
